Ibiro by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwiherera mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zemeje ko abantu bose batuye mu duce twatewe n'ibiza, bagomba kwiherera mu buryo bw'amahwemo cyangwa bakajya babishakiraho.
Amashyaka afite ibyago byo kwandura indwara, yashyizweho amabwiriza akomeye yo kwicungira mu kato.
Abatekereza ko bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi bakaba bamaze igihe gito bavuye mu gihugu cyangwa mu karere k'ubwandu bukabije, bagirwa inama yo kujya mu kato k'iminsi 14 kuva aho bagaragaye.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya ingaruka z'indwara ni ukugabanya cyangwa kugabanya.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, hari ingamba zo kucyirinda zigamije gushaka abantu banduye no kubashyira mu kato, no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kucyirinda no gukingira abandi baturage.
Mu gihe nta cyakorwa ngo indwara ikwirakwize, imihati igenda ihinduka: hagenda hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwizwa ry'iyo ndwara no kugabanya ingaruka igira ku rwego rw'ubuzima no ku baturage
Uburyo bwo kwirinda no guhashya bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Kugira ngo umubare w'abanduye uhinduke munsi ya 1, hakenewe ingamba zikomeye zo kurwanya icyorezo.Iki gikorwa cyo kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara nk'ingingo yo kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara, mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, cyiswe "Flattening the Plague Curve".
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byinshi cyane ku buryo bitakwihanganirwa n'ubuvuzi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu bibazo by'ubudahangarwa bishobora kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibiyobyabwenge harimo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kwirinda isuku, kwambara agapfukamunwa no kwicungira mu kato; ibikorwa by'abaturage bigamije kwirinda abantu ku mubiri, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibirori abantu bahuriraho; uruhare rw'abaturage mu guteza imbere kwakira no kwitabira ibyo bibazo; ndetse n'ibikorwa by'ibidukikije, nko gusukura imyanya y'imbere.
Ibihugu byombi byashyizeho ingamba zo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibizamini byinshi n'imyanya yo kwiherera mu gihugu, ndetse itanga imiburo ku bantu banduye.
Singapore yahaye inkunga abantu bari mu kaga kandi baragaragara ko bari mu kato, ndetse n'ibihano bikomeye ku bantu bananiwe kubikora.
Taiwan kandi yafatiye ibihano abantu batumiza mu mahanga ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'amasuki. Imvugo z'ubushakashatsi z'u Bwongereza na Amerika zigaragaza ko guhagarika (gukumira icyorezo ariko ntikihagarike) no kugabanya (guhindura iterambere ry'icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Imigambi myiza yo kwirinda indwara ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa mu bihumbi byinshi no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa mu bihumbi byinshi no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa n'imitungo y'ubuzima.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya ubwandu bushobora guhabwa umwanya w'icyubahiro ariko bugomba gukingirwa kugeza igihe icyo cyorezo kizakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rwabonetse, uko bizagenda mbere) kuko iyo uburyo bw'ubutegetsi bworoheje bworoheje bushobora kongera kwihuta.
Uburyo bw'igihe kirekire bwo guhangana n'icyorezo buteza ibibazo by'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti igenewe kurwanya COVID-19 ifite icyo imaze, ariko hari ingamba z'uko bayishyiraho harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Gufata imiti yo kugabanya ubukana, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bisaba ubuvuzi bw'ubuhumekero, imitsi y'amaraso n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka, bitewe n'ubukana.
Gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gutuma ingaruka z'ibyo bikoresho zidakora neza.
Hari imiti myinshi yemerewe mbere yo kuvura izindi ndwara z'ubwandu ikomeje gushakishwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
"Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko hari uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo "kuvura indwara z'ubwoko n'ubw'iwabo" bwafasha abantu guhangana n'ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 no guhindura ubuzima bwabo mu buryo bushyize mu gaciro ari ingamba zo guhangana n'indwara y'ibanze.
Ihuriro ry'Igihugu ry'Ubuzima ry'Igihugu (ECDC) n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryasohoye amabwiriza yo kwimura imitungo mu byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira mu gaciro serivisi z'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi ku gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa bidafite ireme aho bishoboka hose, gushyira mu kato abanduye COVID-19 no kwiherera no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwivuza bwa vuba no kongera umubare w'imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'ibitanda bihari, binyuze mu gutoza abakozi.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku bijyanye n'aho umuntu wa mbere wanduye (umurwayi witwa Zero) yahuye n'icyo cyorezo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya mbere cyamenyekanye ku wa 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubaie mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe kitarenze ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus mu mujyi wa Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byombi byiganjemo ibicuruzwa by'ibikomoka ku mazi byo mu bwoko bwa Huwanan, byashoboraga no kugurisha inyamaswa zibayeho. Kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko icyo cyorezo cyavuye kuri kimwe muri ibyo biremwa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko cyanduraga ku nyamaswa. Icyorezo cya pneumonia cyatewe n'impamvu itaramenyekana cyatawe ku wa 26 Ukuboza, gifatwa n'umuganga Zhang Jixian, umujyanama w'ibitaro bya Hubei Provincial Hospital. Yatangaje ku wa 27 Ukuboza ku Wuhan Jiagang CDC (CDC).
"Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan ryagabishije bagenzi babo ko hari "virusi ya corona imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Lee Wenliang, bari barahawe imiburo n'igipolisi kubera ko batangaga amakuru y'ibinyoma, kandi undi muganga witwa Ai Feng, yahawe amabwiriza n'abayobozi be kubera ko yari yarabivuze.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan Municipal Health Authority yahise itanga itangazo ku wa 31 Ukuboza, riha Umuryango w'Abibumbye w'Ubuzima (WHO) amakuru.
Mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, abayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan bamenyesheje abarwayi ba pneumonia batagaragara bihagije, bihagije kugira ngo hatangire iperereza. Mu bihe by'ibanze by'icyorezo, umubare w'abarwayi wiyongereyeho inshuro zigera hafi ku minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi ntara by'u Bushinwa, bifashijwemo n'uko Wuhan yabaye ihuriro ry'imikorere n'ingendo mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa, ndetse n'aho icyorezo cyageze mu bindi bihugu.
Ku wa 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwanditse ko mu munsi umwe honyine habayeho abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, imibare y'ibanze y'abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso, igaragaza ko kugeza ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari imaze kurenga u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abanduye.Ku itariki ya 26 Mata 2020, ku isi hose habayeho ubwandu bwa miliyoni 1.61; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 bakize.
