Mu byo abaturage b'Amerika bakoze harimo kwiherera mu kato (ibivugwa ko ari amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo cyangwa gufungwa) n'amabwiriza yo gufungwa. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu gufungwa mu buryo runaka muri Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miriyoni 1.3 mu Buhinde.
Ku wa 26 Werurwe, abantu babarirwa muri za miriyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bahagaritswe, ariko nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, bariyongereye bagera kuri miriyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; undi utemeza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye COVID-19 ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, Dr. Zhang Jixian yabonye umubare w'abarwayi bafite indwara ya pneumonia ku mpamvu zitazwi. Ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ibyo byamenyeshejwe CDC ya Wuhan Jiangsen, binyuze ku bitaro yakoreragamo.
Ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ibipimo by'ubwoko bw'umurwayi byatangiye gupimwa bigaragaza ko afite virusi ya SARS.
