Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari gukorwa ubushakashatsi ku bipimo by'ubuvuzi birenga 300.
Hari ibigeragezo birindwi byemeza ko hari umuti wa malaria umaze kwemerwa, harimo ibigeragezo bine by'ihydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroguine.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bugizwe ahanini n'imiti itera indwara itera indwara, kandi ibizamini icyenda bya Phase III by'i Remdesvir birategerejwe mu mpera za Mata.
Gusuzuma mu buryo bw'imikorere iterambere ry'ubuvuzi ku bakira COVID-19 ndetse n'abatanze imiti byari bikomeje gukorwa kugeza muri Mata 2020. Inkingo z'uburwayi zisanzwe zigenewe kuvura COVID-19, zirimo Remdesivir, Chloroguine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lobinavir/Ridonavir na Ritonavir ifatanye na Lobinavir/Interferon Be, zirimo gufatwa.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo byerekana ko Remdesivirol ikora neza.
Abarwayi batarahabwa Remdesivir bari bageze ku rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Igerageza ry'icyiciro cya gatatu ry'ubuvuzi ririmo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Chloroguine yari yarigeze gukoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa mu Gashyantare 2020 n'ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, hari ibyo umuntu ukorana na we mu bushakashatsi asaba kongera gusuzuma.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'abo mu Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha Chloroguine.
Ariko kandi, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi bw'indwara cya Wuhan kivuga ko kurya ingano ya buri munsi ya buri mugero w'igiramu imwe ari byo bya mbere by'ubuzima, kandi ko ari byo bibangamira ubuzima bw'abantu incuro ebyiri ibyo bipimo.
Ku wa 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yasohoye uruhushya rwo kwihutira gukoresha Hydroxychloroquine na Chloroguine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura COVID-19. Mu mabwiriza yo mu gitabo cy'Ubushinwa cyo ku wa 7 harimo Interferon, Rivavirin cyangwa Umyfenovir, yakoreshwa mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru atangira avuga ko ari ngombwa ko habaho ingano nyinshi za ribavirin mu kwirinda SARS-CoV-2.
Ubushakashatsi bwa VIVO bwagaragaje ko nitasoxoneide ikenewe cyane mu gihe yagaragaje ko ihindagurika ry'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 ryifashe ku rugero ruto. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukubita imfuruka mbere ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na receptor ya ACE-2.
Ubushakashatsi ku hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroguine, yaba ifitanye isano na asithromycin cyangwa itari ifitanye isano na yo, bufite imipaka myinshi, bituma ubuvuzi butanga icyizere cy'uko buzabasha kubemera nta bushakashatsi bwongeye gukorwa. Oseldamivir ntinaniza SARS-CoV-2 nta ruhare rw'ingenzi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Umuyaga wa cytokine ushobora kuba ikibazo mu bihe bikurikira COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imico ya cytoquin-anti-storm. Dosilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza yo kuvura ya Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, hashingiwe ku mwanzuro w'ubushakashatsi muto.
Nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ari ingirakamaro mu barwayi barwaye cyane, iki cyiciro cy'igeragezwa ku rwego rw'igihugu cyakozwe mu Butaliyani, cyakozwe mu byiciro bibiri.
Gushyira hamwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku maraso ya Ferrit kugira ngo bamenye ibihuhusi bya cytokine, byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu gihe hari intambwe zimwe na zimwe nk'izo zatumye hapfa bamwe mu barwayi.
Mu 2017, FDA yemeje interleukin-6 receptor based on studies of a subsequent infection for the treatment of a steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome (steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome) by'umwihariko mu gihe cy'uburwayi bw'indwara z'umubiri.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya idashidikanywaho y'uko dosilismap ari umuti mwiza wo kwivuza kuri CRS.
Guhindurira abandi bakenera imiti ihumura kandi ivangwa ikorwa n'umubiri w'abakize COVID-19 mu gihe bakeneye imiti ihumura, ni uburyo bw'irinda gukingira indwara z'indwara.
Iki gikorwa cyageragejwe na Sarz, ariko nta cyo byatangaje.
Kwifata ku ngufu ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora, ku buryo imiti itagira icyo ikora ya protini ishobora guhuza umutekano kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, ubundi buryo bwo kuvura poroteyine, urugero nk'icyitotoxicity yo mu ngirabuzimafatizo no/cyangwa bacocytosis, bushoboka.
Ibindi byiciro by'ubuvuzi bw'indwara z'ubusambanyi, urugero nko gukoresha indwara z'ubusambanyi z'indwara z'ubusambanyi, biri mu iterambere.
Umusaruro w'amazi y'imvura y'amaraso yavanywe mu barwayi bakiriye ndetse n'ayandi afite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya iyi ndwara, ushobora kwiyongera ku buryo bworoshye.
